title: last final project of the semester!
content: Today is my last day of the fall semester! After a long and trecherous two months of being overloaded with projects and homework, I have finally made it to the light at the end of the tunnel. Perhaps I should get a slice of strawbery shortcake as a reward?

title: final seasons
content: Finals is upon us! I have had the fortune of completely finishing one course of the six courses this semester. I only have to worry about the remaining 5 classes, but I know that I have at least two guaranteed A's. I can't wait till this semester is finally over. I wonder if I'll ever get an email response from the Study Abroad program.
